                    </div>
                    <span>Battle is one of the more accesable books on the Battle of the Bulge. It has been around long enough that I own it in a 0.75 paperback. Like Ryan's Longest Day this book is a collection of focused stories within the frame work of a battle narrative. It's main virtue is it's readability.</span>
                  
              
